Markets available on Kraken Pro
Not all currencies available on Kraken can be directly traded for one another. This article lists all tradable currency pairs (also referred to as markets) on our exchange. You can however buy, sell and convert any asset to any other asset, with some restrictions, when using the Buy Crypto widget, and our Kraken mobile app.
Currency availability
Some currencies listed below are not available in specific countries.
